1
00:00:08,600 --> 00:00:09,440
Xiaochao,

2
00:00:10,120 --> 00:00:11,120
are you moving?

3
00:00:13,280 --> 00:00:14,160
I will miss you.

4
00:00:14,160 --> 00:00:15,820
Please don't forget me, okay?

5
00:00:21,520 --> 00:00:22,960
Xiaochao, what's wrong?

6
00:00:26,280 --> 00:00:27,720
Xiaochao, what's wrong?

7
00:01:32,120 --> 00:01:32,920
Lin Jiaming.

8
00:01:54,960 --> 00:01:55,720
Mr. Bai.

9
00:01:56,200 --> 00:01:57,200
Look at the time.

10
00:01:57,200 --> 00:01:58,259
You're late again.

11
00:02:00,160 --> 00:02:02,160
I had some things to deal with at home.

12
00:02:02,160 --> 00:02:03,080
I'm sorry.

13
00:02:05,200 --> 00:02:08,530
Things are very unpleasant on both sides at the foundation.

14
00:02:09,759 --> 00:02:11,200
This Li Weiguo,

15
00:02:11,760 --> 00:02:13,290
is he still working for you?

16
00:02:13,840 --> 00:02:14,400
Yes.

17
00:02:15,200 --> 00:02:16,040
Since he's your man,

18
00:02:16,040 --> 00:02:17,370
you handle it yourself.

19
00:02:18,240 --> 00:02:19,120
Remember,

20
00:02:20,240 --> 00:02:22,040
don't let it affect the company.

21
00:02:27,360 --> 00:02:28,220
Have you eaten?

22
00:02:31,680 --> 00:02:32,960
N-no.

23
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:34,480
Here,

24
00:02:35,720 --> 00:02:36,680
let me do it.

25
00:02:38,640 --> 00:02:40,170
Thank you. Enjoy your meal.

26
00:02:40,960 --> 00:02:41,560
Eat.

27
00:02:42,800 --> 00:02:43,320
Mr. Bai,

28
00:02:43,320 --> 00:02:44,280
today...

29
00:02:45,079 --> 00:02:47,200
why did you go to such expense for me?

30
00:02:48,240 --> 00:02:49,040
Not at all.

31
00:02:49,680 --> 00:02:52,410
I just ordered the dishes you usually like to eat.

32
00:02:52,560 --> 00:02:53,160
Eat.

33
00:02:56,200 --> 00:02:56,920
Old Li,

34
00:02:57,440 --> 00:02:58,440
how long have you been with me?

35
00:02:58,440 --> 00:02:59,640
Has it been ten years?

36
00:02:59,840 --> 00:03:00,880
Twelve years.

37
00:03:02,880 --> 00:03:04,360
Time flies.

38
00:03:05,120 --> 00:03:05,840
So,

39
00:03:06,440 --> 00:03:08,280
you've helped me for so many years.

40
00:03:08,280 --> 00:03:10,160
Are you satisfied with the treatment and everything?

41
00:03:10,160 --> 00:03:11,280
Satisfied.

42
00:03:11,920 --> 00:03:12,440
Mr. Bai,

43
00:03:13,240 --> 00:03:14,880
you treat me like...

44
00:03:14,880 --> 00:03:15,920
family.

45
00:03:16,600 --> 00:03:18,260
On Miss Bai's tenth birthday,

46
00:03:19,200 --> 00:03:20,560
you even invited me and Xiaohao

47
00:03:20,560 --> 00:03:21,820
to your home as guests.

48
00:03:23,800 --> 00:03:24,440
At that time,

49
00:03:24,440 --> 00:03:26,720
Xiaohao, Xiaoqiu, and Jiaming

50
00:03:26,720 --> 00:03:28,040
were all good friends.

51
00:03:28,040 --> 00:03:30,240
They played and joked around together.

52
00:03:31,200 --> 00:03:32,800
I wouldn't dare say friends.

53
00:03:36,840 --> 00:03:38,240
Xiaohao was a good kid.

54
00:03:39,800 --> 00:03:40,800
I didn't expect so many things

55
00:03:40,800 --> 00:03:42,000
to happen after that.

56
00:03:43,800 --> 00:03:44,400
By the way,

57
00:03:45,040 --> 00:03:46,840
the Lin Group wants to set up

58
00:03:47,200 --> 00:03:48,730
a foundation in Qiongzhou.

59
00:03:48,960 --> 00:03:50,720
It can be considered doing something for Xiaohao.

60
00:03:50,720 --> 00:03:51,520
Thank you.

61
00:03:52,240 --> 00:03:54,640
But I heard you guys had an unpleasant falling out.

62
00:03:54,640 --> 00:03:56,500
Is there some misunderstanding?

63
00:03:57,440 --> 00:03:58,280
Rumors...

64
00:03:58,280 --> 00:03:59,920
I've heard some,

65
00:03:59,920 --> 00:04:01,280
but... but I...

66
00:04:01,280 --> 00:04:02,880
I really don't believe them.

67
00:04:03,720 --> 00:04:04,640
Look,

68
00:04:04,640 --> 00:04:06,100
whether it's the Lin Group

69
00:04:06,360 --> 00:04:07,880
or the Lin father and son,

70
00:04:07,880 --> 00:04:10,560
they've been genuinely good to our family.

71
00:04:10,560 --> 00:04:11,440
I...

72
00:04:11,440 --> 00:04:12,800
