73
00:04:12,800 --> 00:04:15,000
How could there be a misunderstanding?

74
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:15,760
Well,

75
00:04:16,079 --> 00:04:17,000
it's okay.

76
00:04:17,560 --> 00:04:19,490
If you really feel uncomfortable,

77
00:04:19,600 --> 00:04:20,399
want to change jobs,

78
00:04:20,399 --> 00:04:22,460
or have any financial difficulties,

79
00:04:22,760 --> 00:04:24,880
Or if you just want to go out for a walk and relax,

80
00:04:24,880 --> 00:04:26,000
you can tell me.

81
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:26,760
I will support you.

82
00:04:26,760 --> 00:04:27,760
M-Mr. Bai.

83
00:04:28,720 --> 00:04:31,160
I know it's my fault for being late recently.

84
00:04:31,160 --> 00:04:31,720
But please rest assured.

85
00:04:31,720 --> 00:04:33,520
Once I handle my family matters,

86
00:04:33,520 --> 00:04:34,960
I promise to be on call,

87
00:04:34,960 --> 00:04:37,360
and I will never let it affect my work again.

88
00:04:43,320 --> 00:04:45,560
I was also negligent about your family affairs.

89
00:04:45,560 --> 00:04:46,680
N-No, no.

90
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:51,920
Please take this as a token of my care.

91
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:52,520
No, no, I can't.

92
00:04:52,520 --> 00:04:53,680
I-I can't.

93
00:04:53,680 --> 00:04:54,440
I really can't accept this.

94
00:04:54,440 --> 00:04:55,320
Just take it.

95
00:04:56,200 --> 00:04:58,400
Buy some supplements or something for your wife.

96
00:04:58,400 --> 00:04:59,480
I really can't take this money.

97
00:04:59,480 --> 00:05:01,160
Thank you, Mr. Bai. Thank you.

98
00:05:01,160 --> 00:05:02,320
Thank you. Thank you.

99
00:05:02,320 --> 00:05:04,180
I've already taken it out anyway.

100
00:05:04,320 --> 00:05:05,400
You can either leave it here,

101
00:05:05,400 --> 00:05:06,460
or take it with you.

102
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:07,460
Take your pick.

103
00:05:15,520 --> 00:05:16,120
Thank you.

104
00:05:16,960 --> 00:05:18,020
Thank you, Mr. Bai.

105
00:05:18,200 --> 00:05:18,920
Let's eat.

106
00:05:24,200 --> 00:05:24,960
Here.

107
00:05:26,240 --> 00:05:27,360
Thank you.

108
00:05:30,600 --> 00:05:31,200
Let's eat.

109
00:05:31,880 --> 00:05:33,040
Thank you, Mr. Bai.

110
00:06:15,720 --> 00:06:16,560
Chao.

111
00:06:17,280 --> 00:06:18,810
Want some instant noodles?

112
00:06:19,680 --> 00:06:20,480
You...

113
00:06:20,480 --> 00:06:21,540
What are you doing?

114
00:06:32,640 --> 00:06:33,400
Yu, Yu.

115
00:06:33,400 --> 00:06:34,800
Yu, wake up. Wake up.

116
00:06:35,240 --> 00:06:36,640
Chao is acting really weird.

117
00:06:36,640 --> 00:06:37,440
You're the weird one.

118
00:06:37,440 --> 00:06:38,360
Staying up so late.

119
00:06:38,360 --> 00:06:39,240
He went out.

120
00:06:39,240 --> 00:06:39,920
Let's go check on him.

121
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:40,640
Hurry up.

122
00:06:40,640 --> 00:06:42,320
Are you crazy?

123
00:06:43,680 --> 00:06:45,200
Hurry up, let's go.

124
00:06:45,200 --> 00:06:46,400
Okay, okay, okay.

125
00:06:48,320 --> 00:06:49,280
I'll go after him first.

126
00:06:49,280 --> 00:06:50,560
Yu, follow me.

127
00:06:54,040 --> 00:06:54,560
No.

128
00:06:54,560 --> 00:06:56,720
Why did you follow Chao when he went out?

129
00:06:56,720 --> 00:06:58,040
He ignores me when I talk to him.

130
00:06:58,040 --> 00:06:59,760
He just stares straight ahead and keeps walking.

131
00:06:59,760 --> 00:07:01,240
Don't you think it's strange?

132
00:07:01,240 --> 00:07:02,280
And when have you ever seen

133
00:07:02,280 --> 00:07:03,320
Chao like this?

134
00:07:03,320 --> 00:07:04,320
Right.

135
00:07:07,440 --> 00:07:08,800
Chao is different

136
00:07:09,640 --> 00:07:10,720
from before.

137
00:07:13,120 --> 00:07:14,080
That's true.

138
00:07:15,240 --> 00:07:16,600
He doesn't sleep at night

139
00:07:16,600 --> 00:07:19,260
and doesn't remember anything when he wakes up.

140
00:07:19,800 --> 00:07:20,640
Do you think

141
00:07:21,040 --> 00:07:22,560
he might have

142
00:07:22,560 --> 00:07:24,040
sleepwalking?

143
00:07:24,040 --> 00:07:25,400
That makes sense.

144
00:07:25,400 --> 00:07:26,360
Yu, in four years of college,

145
00:07:26,360 --> 00:07:27,960
didn't you notice he has this condition?

146
00:07:27,960 --> 00:07:29,720
No. He wasn't like this before.

147
00:07:29,720 --> 00:07:31,000
It was only after Weihao left

148
00:07:31,000 --> 00:07:32,460
that he became so strange.

149
00:07:32,880 --> 00:07:35,040
It's sad when a friend dies.

150
00:07:35,040 --> 00:07:37,440
They say you shouldn't wake a sleepwalker.

151
00:07:37,920 --> 00:07:39,320
Then what should we do?

152
00:07:39,320 --> 00:07:40,320
Let's follow him first

153
00:07:40,320 --> 00:07:41,200
and see what he's up to.

154
00:07:41,200 --> 00:07:42,840
We'll take him back when there are fewer people.

155
00:07:42,840 --> 00:07:43,480
Okay.

156
00:07:43,480 --> 00:07:44,040
Let's go.

157
00:07:46,920 --> 00:07:47,720
Wait.

158
00:07:47,720 --> 00:07:50,050
Do sleepwalkers cross at traffic lights?

159
00:08:00,840 --> 00:08:02,240
Let's go.

160
00:08:27,640 --> 00:08:29,600
What is he buying?

161
00:08:29,840 --> 00:08:30,760
It looks like

162
00:08:30,760 --> 00:08:31,720
Qingbuliang.

163
00:08:31,720 --> 00:08:32,760
What?

164
00:08:32,760 --> 00:08:33,320
No.

165
00:08:36,840 --> 00:08:38,480
Qingbuliang.

166
00:08:38,480 --> 00:08:39,200
Yeah.

167
00:08:39,200 --> 00:08:40,240
Are you sure?

168
00:08:40,559 --> 00:08:41,799
What's wrong with that?

169
00:08:41,799 --> 00:08:43,760
Chao never eats sweets.

170
00:08:44,320 --> 00:08:45,360
That's strange.

171
00:08:45,680 --> 00:08:46,880
Didn't I last time...

172
00:08:55,880 --> 00:08:56,760
Here you go.

173
00:08:58,000 --> 00:08:58,660
Here you go.

174
00:08:58,840 --> 00:08:59,720
Thanks.

175
00:08:59,720 --> 00:09:00,650
You're welcome.

176
00:09:01,640 --> 00:09:03,920
Do you think a sleepwalker can pay?

177
00:09:04,520 --> 00:09:06,650
Does he look like a sleepwalker to you?

178
00:09:10,960 --> 00:09:12,280
Did we get it wrong?

179
00:09:12,600 --> 00:09:14,400
But I still feel like this Chao

180
00:09:14,600 --> 00:09:15,760
is very strange.

181
00:09:16,680 --> 00:09:18,140
I can hear you two talking.

182
00:09:19,120 --> 00:09:19,840
Chao.

183
00:09:19,840 --> 00:09:21,280
You came out for a midnight snack.

184
00:09:21,280 --> 00:09:22,400
Why didn't you bring us?

185
00:09:22,400 --> 00:09:22,800
Right?

186
00:09:22,800 --> 00:09:23,880
What did you call me?

187
00:09:23,880 --> 00:09:24,800
I called you Chao.

188
00:09:24,800 --> 00:09:25,400
If I don't call you Chao,

189
00:09:25,400 --> 00:09:26,840
what else should I call you?

190
00:09:26,840 --> 00:09:28,840
Chao, do you remember who we are?

191
00:09:28,840 --> 00:09:29,880
You also called me Chao.

192
00:09:29,880 --> 00:09:30,320
Yeah.

193
00:09:30,320 --> 00:09:31,400
Of course I know.

194
00:09:31,400 --> 00:09:33,060
You two are my best roommates.

195
00:09:33,200 --> 00:09:34,000
He remembers.

196
00:09:34,000 --> 00:09:35,120
No problem.

197
00:09:35,600 --> 00:09:36,560
My treat.

198
00:09:36,560 --> 00:09:37,920
This is my favorite.

199
00:09:37,920 --> 00:09:38,640
Thanks.

200
00:09:38,640 --> 00:09:39,570
You're welcome.

201
00:09:41,160 --> 00:09:41,840
Try it.

202
00:09:42,280 --> 00:09:42,960
Okay, thanks.

203
00:09:42,960 --> 00:09:43,890
You're welcome.

204
00:09:45,800 --> 00:09:47,730
He must be possessed by something.

205
00:09:49,880 --> 00:09:51,520
I have to say, it's actually really good.

206
00:09:51,520 --> 00:09:52,240
Right?

207
00:09:52,600 --> 00:09:54,040
It's so good.

208
00:09:55,320 --> 00:09:57,250
He must be possessed by something.

209
00:09:57,480 --> 00:09:58,640
So cute.

210
00:10:00,120 --> 00:10:01,320
Let's take a picture.

211
00:10:01,640 --> 00:10:02,480
Of course.

212
00:10:02,880 --> 00:10:03,400
Is it okay?

213
00:10:03,400 --> 00:10:04,080
Sure.

214
00:10:04,360 --> 00:10:05,560
Alright then.

215
00:10:05,560 --> 00:10:06,440
Thank you.

216
00:10:06,440 --> 00:10:08,600
But I still feel like something is wrong.

217
00:10:08,600 --> 00:10:09,160
Come on.

218
00:10:10,120 --> 00:10:11,040
Smile.

219
00:10:13,080 --> 00:10:14,080
Three.

220
00:10:16,680 --> 00:10:17,680
Good.

221
00:10:17,680 --> 00:10:18,840
Sleepwalking.

222
00:10:18,840 --> 00:10:20,200
I must be sleepwalking.

223
00:10:20,720 --> 00:10:21,960
I have to say,

224
00:10:21,960 --> 00:10:24,000
I actually really like Chao like this.

225
00:10:24,000 --> 00:10:24,920
I like you too.

226
00:10:27,000 --> 00:10:27,960
So cute.

227
00:10:28,280 --> 00:10:29,000
Cute.

228
00:10:30,120 --> 00:10:31,560
Can you always call me Chao?

229
00:10:31,560 --> 00:10:33,120
Of course.

230
00:10:33,120 --> 00:10:34,000
Pinky swear.

231
00:10:34,000 --> 00:10:34,720
Chao.

232
00:10:35,200 --> 00:10:35,760
Chao.

233
00:10:36,240 --> 00:10:37,040
Chao.

234
00:10:37,960 --> 00:10:38,440
No.

235
00:10:38,920 --> 00:10:39,450
Oh my god.

236
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:42,440
Chao,

237
00:10:42,600 --> 00:10:43,600
let's stop eating this.

238
00:10:43,600 --> 00:10:45,440
I'll take you to a really good barbecue place.

239
00:10:45,440 --> 00:10:46,800
Let's go.

240
00:10:47,520 --> 00:10:47,880
Guys,

241
00:10:47,880 --> 00:10:48,680
