244
00:10:53,880 --> 00:10:54,920
Two madmen.

245
00:10:55,480 --> 00:10:56,760
I must be crazy.

246
00:11:03,960 --> 00:11:04,560
Hurry up.

247
00:11:06,560 --> 00:11:07,600
Who is it?

248
00:11:11,040 --> 00:11:12,400
Who ran out?

249
00:11:12,760 --> 00:11:14,020
Don't let me catch you.

250
00:11:19,680 --> 00:11:22,040
Let's go.

251
00:11:26,480 --> 00:11:28,120
Keep your voice down.

252
00:11:28,760 --> 00:11:30,320
This is so exciting.

253
00:11:31,120 --> 00:11:32,080
But then again,

254
00:11:32,600 --> 00:11:34,320
