272
00:11:58,080 --> 00:11:59,160
Come on. Wait for me, Chao.

273
00:11:59,160 --> 00:12:00,820
Let me change into my pajamas.

274
00:12:08,000 --> 00:12:09,060
What are you doing?

275
00:12:09,560 --> 00:12:10,360
