276
00:12:10,360 --> 00:12:11,520
I'm sleeping.

277
00:12:13,720 --> 00:12:15,160
Why are you sleeping in my bed?

278
00:12:15,160 --> 00:12:16,880
You told me to come up yesterday.

279
00:12:16,880 --> 00:12:17,960
Am I crazy?

280
00:12:18,400 --> 00:12:20,120
Could I not sleep alone or something?

281
00:12:20,120 --> 00:12:20,800
Yeah.

282
00:12:20,800 --> 00:12:22,360
You said you couldn't sleep and wanted to chat,

283
00:12:22,360 --> 00:12:24,040
so you asked me to come over.

284
00:12:24,040 --> 00:12:26,520
Do I look like someone who likes to chat?

285
00:12:26,520 --> 00:12:28,720
I'll give you three seconds to get down.

286
00:12:29,520 --> 00:12:30,000
Chao.

287
00:12:30,920 --> 00:12:31,800
I know.

288
00:12:32,680 --> 00:12:34,610
You were sleepwalking last night.

289
00:12:34,640 --> 00:12:36,100
You're sleeping in my bed.

290
00:12:36,440 --> 00:12:38,320
Are you sleepwalking or am I?

291
00:12:38,680 --> 00:12:39,520
It's absolutely true.

292
00:12:39,520 --> 00:12:40,120
Chao.

293
00:12:40,400 --> 00:12:42,320
Not only did you leave the school yesterday,

294
00:12:42,320 --> 00:12:45,780
but you also went to the convenience store at the gate to buy...

