591
00:30:54,640 --> 00:30:56,640
have done every bad thing possible.

592
00:30:56,800 --> 00:30:58,260
They eat well, sleep well,

593
00:30:58,880 --> 00:31:00,200
lie in bed at home,

594
00:31:00,400 --> 00:31:02,730
and count money until their hands go soft.

595
00:31:02,800 --> 00:31:04,400
Not only will I keep working,

596
00:31:06,000 --> 00:31:07,800
but I will also watch them, one by one,

597
00:31:07,800 --> 00:31:09,330
have their families ruined

598
00:31:09,720 --> 00:31:11,240
and wish they were dead.

599
00:31:12,200 --> 00:31:13,460
I don't see it that way.

600
00:31:14,000 --> 00:31:16,760
I actually hope they live a long life.

601
00:31:18,360 --> 00:31:19,560
When the boss feasts,

602
00:31:19,560 --> 00:31:20,800
the subordinates get to drink soup.

603
00:31:20,800 --> 00:31:23,000
It's good for all of us.

604
00:31:23,360 --> 00:31:24,800
You still want to feast.

605
00:31:25,680 --> 00:31:27,640
Look at these people you've brought recently.

606
00:31:27,640 --> 00:31:28,800
Every single one of them,

607
00:31:28,800 --> 00:31:30,930
it's the same few faces back and forth.

608
00:31:31,040 --> 00:31:32,800
Haven't brought in any new goods lately?

609
00:31:32,800 --> 00:31:34,440
There are new goods.

610
00:31:35,040 --> 00:31:35,880
It's just that

611
00:31:36,280 --> 00:31:37,360
one I dare not use,

612
00:31:38,160 --> 00:31:39,960
and the other I don't want to use.

613
00:31:47,560 --> 00:31:48,620
Isn't this Shasha?

614
00:31:48,920 --> 00:31:50,080
Her name is Yueyue.

615
00:31:50,080 --> 00:31:50,800
Yueyue?

616
00:31:53,600 --> 00:31:54,920
They look exactly the same.
